title: Top EU Court says that US-EU data transfer deal is invalid
text:
LUXEMBOURG/BRUSSELS: A system enabling data transfers from the European Union to the United States by thousands of companies is invalid, the highest EU court said on Tuesday in a landmark ruling.
"The Court of Justice declares that the Commissionâ€™s U.S. Safe Harbour Decision is invalid," it said in a statement on Tuesday.
(Reporting by Michele Sinner and Julia Fioretti; editing by Barbara Lewis)
